                    <p class="audience">Suggested Audiences: Grades 1 to 5</p>
                    <p> If Only You Knew  is a heartfelt story about a boy named Joey who wakes up every morning with the hopes of making his mother proud with all that he learns in school. But then he finds himself being bullied in not just one but all his classes every day by some fellow classmates. He's unable to concentrate on his school work and feels scared and alone, not knowing where to go or who to tell. Find out how Joey learns that finding his courage and facing his fears would bring him the greatest joy within himself, at school and at home, to last him a lifetime.</p>
                    
